(102, 3, '2014-02-09 20:33:27', '2014-02-09 20:33:27', '<!--:en-->At DID we create strategies, research, products and services supported by an open design process. We use design as a multidimensional tool to create value for companies, institutions, social organisations and individuals to help them reach their development goals.\r\n\r\nWe collaborate with our clients in a wide array of projects of diverse scale and scope. Furthermore our independent initiatives allow us to identify new business opportunities by exploring new markets and services. DID supports its action in the expertise of a professional network that over the past 10 years, has played a key role in the integration of design thinking in to social, economical and political activities  INSERT INTO `wp_terms` (`term_id`, `name`, `slug`, `term_group`) VALUES
